Attractions.description: Long hidden on the fringe of Florida's Gulf coast and overlooked by developers until well into the 1880s, Naples' catalyst for settlement finally arrived forty years later when two rival railroads rolled into town within ten days of each other. Set in Naples' restored Seaboard Air Line Railway passenger station, the Naples Depot Museum welcomes visitors back to the railroading boom days of the Roaring Twenties and explains how generations of Southwest Floridians used technology and transportation to conquer a vast and seemingly impenetrable frontier.Seminole dugout canoes, a mule wagon, antique swamp buggy, restored rail cars and exciting interactive exhibits tell the story of how trade and travel transformed Naples from a napping village of 300 souls into today's glittering Gulf coast resort. The Naples Depot Museum is listed on the National Register of Historic Places and is conveniently located in downtown Naples.

Attractions.description: Ankrolab Brewing Company is passionate about bringing our patrons the finest beer we can produce. That passion begins with beer’s most important ingredient- water. Generally you will find that the gallery has 40 to 50 local artists' work on display and it refreshes about half of the inventory the second Monday of every month. ​ Participating artists offer oil, pastel, acrylic and watercolor paintings, photography, ceramics, glass, textiles, jewelry, wood, statues, seasonal cards fiber art and more. PLEASE NOTE THAT THE GALLERY IS CLOSED THE 2ND TUESDAY OF EACH MONTH FOR INVENTORY PURPOSES

Restaurants.name: Mediterrano
Restaurants.description: Welcome to Mediterrano where we take a coastal approach to the splendor of Mediterranean cuisine. Our valued customers will find tantalizing dishes from the coasts of Spain, Greece, Italy, Morocco and many more of the Mediterranean sea's bordering countries. We invite you to come experience our culinary vision for coastal Mediterranean, where explosive flavor profiles are delicately balanced through a fresh regional platform. Mediterrano, where exquisite food is complimented with top class hospitality.

Restaurants.name: Van Van Cuban Cafe

photo.caption: Anything you order, you will love!

Restaurants.description: Welcome to Van Van Cuban Cafe! Our restaurant offers food lovers the opportunity to experience the authentic flavors of Cuban Cuisine in a stylish way. Our menu focuses on traditional Cuban preparations, but also displays some famous international dishes. Van Van Cuban Cafe is the place where families and friends can gather and celebrate while enjoying our homemade delights.

Restaurants.name: Lamoraga
Restaurants.description: Lamoraga Restaurant showcases a Mediterranean Fusion and Tapas Cuisine restaurant in Naples, Florida. We offer a wide variety of international dishes, delicious food, fresh seafood, and refreshing cocktails.

Restaurants.name: Bha! Bha! Persian Bistro
Restaurants.description: This is an elegant high end and fine dinning innovative and classic "Persian" bistro for adults. Food: It offers arrays of faboulas dishes with roots in Iran but with modern Florida flair and influnce. The menu is vast, it concentrates on savory elegant braised lamb in many different varieties, Eggplant, fresh Fl seafood, grilled kebabs of beef, chicken. Lamb rule here. Other dishes such as duck, quail and seafood with exquisite Persian saffron rices are all fabulously tempting and present here. Full bar. Excellent wine list (No BYOB) signature boutique wines. Dress code: Florida casual but elegant and proper please. No tank tops or flip flops. No kids menu, No strollers. No crying babies please. Outside requests: (weather permitting) are accpted but not guaranteed. Dine under the stars in this highly acclaimed international destination. Bha! Bha! Bistro is referred to as " Jewel of the Crown" of the cosmopolitan 5th Ave in Naples FL. NYT calls it: "Persian Perfection"

Restaurants.name: Caffe dell'Amore
Restaurants.description: Italian Restaurant in Naples, Florida Remember that wonderful vacation you took to Italy with your beloved awhile back? You strolled through the streets taking in the sites, the art, the culture, and the joy of living around you. You stopped to eat in one of the many wonderful trattoria, intimate and romantic, savoring the best Italian food, drinking great wine, talking with loved ones and just enjoying life. Caffe dell'Amore allows you to recreate that experience. Our Italian restaurant in Naples, Florida, serves authentic meals made with generations-old recipes passed down from chef to chef. We cook with love and passion, offering you a taste of Italy while you enjoy the company of loves ones in an intimate setting. A Fine Dining Italian Restaurant Inspired by the great Italian tradition of quality at the table and in the glass, we are dedicated to seeking out the best ingredients for our dishes.
Restaurants.address: 1400 Gulf Shore Blvd N, Ste 154 Ste 154, Naples, FL 34102

Restaurants.name: T-Michaels Steak and Lobster
Restaurants.description: T-Michaels Steak and Lobster is a fine dining Waterfront restaurant on Venetian Bay in Naples, Florida! Our Daily Specials highlight locally caught fish with fresh ingredients, and our Wine list will be ever evolving with featured bottles weekly from around the globe.

Restaurants.name: Rumba Cuban Cafe

Since opening in 2014, Rumba has delighted guests from all over the world. Bringing a little piece of Cuba closer to beautiful Naples, Florida.

Restaurants.name: Brooks Burgers

Come try one of our unique burgers and join our family!

Restaurants.name: Noodles Italian Cafe & Sushi Bar
Restaurants.description: The Original Noodles since 1991, not the chain franchise. Local Owners Matt and Seth, Invite your family to join our family at Noodles Italian Cafe & Sushi Bar for a wonderful array of mouthwatering dishes for you to choose from. Homemade in house fresh pasta, fresh in house prepared desserts like Tiramisu made with real espresso coffee and imported Italian lady fingers. Our newly designed concept offers upscale Italian fare and classic favorites. Along with traditional sushi freshly made by our fantastic authentic trained sushi chefs. Try our own sushi creations like the "Big Daddy roll' filled with all our fresh fish and lightly tempura fried, or one of the traditional sushi creations like Tuna Tataki, prepared with "aaa grade" high quality tuna. Come and feast with us and all the flavors of the world.

Restaurants.name: Fuse Global Cuisine

Enjoy the fresh breezes of Naples Bay on our outdoor dining area. EJ’s is a great place to meet your friends, enjoy a bottomless cup of coffee and casually visit for awhile. Get your work done or meet with business clients. EJ’s offers free WIFI. Pet friendly restaurant.

Restaurants.name: Captain & Krewe
Restaurants.description: Captain & Krewe serves up superb fresh seafood, prepared classically, in a relaxed and casual environment. Come as you are and enjoy a meal that rivals any fine dining restaurant. We also have a variety of beer, wine and non-seafood options available.

Restaurants.name: Truluck's Ocean's Finest Seafood & Crab
Restaurants.description: Fresh redefined. Our chefs honor and elevate seafood dishes with superior ingredients, precise execution, and classic presentation. We are committed to serving the ocean’s finest seafood and fresh Florida Stone crab. From the traps to your table in less than 24 hours. Delight in the art of the cocktail, remarkable wines, captivating ambience and the service you deserve. Your table is waiting.

Restaurants.name: La Trattoria
Restaurants.description: Located in the heart of Downtown Naples, La Trattoria has combined old world charm with a sense of family. Locally Owned and Operated, the familiar faces that run La Trattoria are the same that have been voted nationally “Travelers Best Everyday Dining “ a couple doors down at Caffe Milano. Luca Di Falco has extended his warm welcome down the street through the arms of La Trattoria. By Partnering with Massimiliano Tonni, an award winning craft cocktail creator, and by far one of the best front of the house managers in town and Domenico Foraggio, a third generation Pizza Chef from Naples Italy. La Trattoria offers an extensive selection of real Neapolitan style Personal Pizzas, Chef Domenico siting the reason it’s so Delicious is the simplicity of the ingredients and the many topping combinations the restaurant offers. La Trattoria also offers a full Pasta menu with options that make your mouth water and a unique Imported Beer Menu.

Restaurants.name: First Watch
Restaurants.description: First Watch specializes in delicious creations freshly-prepared to order. Their fresh, award-winning Breakfast, Brunch and Lunch dishes are made using only the best ingredients without the use of heat lamps or deep fryers. The best part is their creative menu features traditional favorites like omelets, pancakes, salads and sandwiches.

Restaurants.name: Ocean Prime
Restaurants.description: Ocean Prime is an award winning modern American restaurant and lounge from renowned restaurateur Cameron Mitchell. With stunning settings, a vibrant energy, an impressive menu of seafood and steaks and truly exceptional service, Ocean Prime is an ideal place to socialize, talk business, celebrate and indulge.

Restaurants.name: Osteria Tulia
Restaurants.description: Osteria Tulia is Naples, Florida's first osteria, serving exquisitely prepared Italian peasant cuisine in the ambiance of a lovingly restored Italian farmhouse. Osteria Tulia is the vision of Sicilian-born Chef/Partner Vincenzo Betulia, a long-time Old Naples chef whose flavorful dishes have earned top culinary accolades and a passionate international following.

Restaurants.name: USS Nemo Restaurant
Restaurants.description: A stylized sort of nautical setting, USS Nemo's cool, comfortable blue interior gives one just a hint of the old "Voyage to the Bottom of Sea" motif with round brass portholes and a mock periscope. The menu definitely appeals to those with a taste for the exotic as it successfully marries a seafood cornucopia with Asian cuisine. The service is impeccable and the entrees are styled in drop-dead gorgeous fashion. The Bento Boxes are marvelous conversation starters. Even the pickled ginger is made to look like a piece of art. It's easy to see why USS Nemo is popular with the crowd of the going place.

Restaurants.name: Hobnob Kitchen & Bar
Restaurants.description: For creative American cuisine that is both fresh and simple, look no further than Naples own HobNob Kitchen & Bar. Executive Chef Tony Biagetti and Chef du Cuisine Jeremy Caprari are in constant collaboration to bring new trends and new takes on traditional American cuisine right to your table. Using the freshest and highest quality ingredients that are often sourced locally, they're able to offer up a truly unforgettable meal! For interesting takes on traditional favorites, order the Snapper in Crazy Water with tomato, fennel, and soft polenta or even our popular Meyer Lemon Short Ribs with lemon risotto, escarole, and pine nut gremolata. But HobNob Kitchen & Bar isn't only known for our incredible food, we have a truly impeccable bar. Designed for comfort and aided by swagger, it's the perfect spot to meet for a drink with friends! We have all of your favorite libations as well as a craft beer menu (including our own HobNob Ale!) And an ever-evolving wine list. Stop by and enjoy our daily happy hour from 4-6pm with half-off wells and wines and a special happy hour menu. When you're in the mood for a delicious, innovative, fresh meal, join us at HobNob Kitchen & Bar! Dinner Monday - Saturday 5 P.M - 10 P.M Sunday 5 P.M - 9 P.M

Restaurants.name: Skillets

photo.caption: Start your day with scratch made pancakes. We start wtih flour, eggs and build the batter that gives our pancakes their distinctive flavor.

Restaurants.description: Great food made from scratch! The Skillets brand has proudly served the finest breakfast and lunch for 25 years with locations throughout Southern Florida. All of our delicious dishes are scratch-made from the finest ingredients available. Fresh-squeezed juices in frosted mugs, our custom-blend coffee beans ground per brew, homemade breads, biscuits, and scones, always fresh, seasonal fruits, skillets dishes, omelets, eggs any style, slow-roasted corned beef hash, thick-cut smokehouse bacon, french toast, light as feather waffles, crepes, and over-the-top pancakes. Lunch has a wide array of sandwiches, salads, wraps, tacos, panini, platters, and combos - all served in a beautiful setting by a staff that really cares about your satisfaction and happiness. If you haven't been to Skillets, it's time you come by and taste the difference. Dine In, Takeout, Delivery, and Catering are available.

Friendly service, excellent food and a great atmosphere are our specialties. We are famous for our sea bass, prawns and snapper dishes.

Restaurants.name: Jimmy P's Charred - Naples
Restaurants.description: As you enter through the front doors, you will know that you have arrived in the finest steak and chop house when the sweet smoky air from the in- house smoker reaches your nose. The visible adjacent butcher shop allows our guests to see the action of our expert meat cutters readying the evening's special cuts. We will still offer a few seats in the butcher shop for the casual lunch crowd. Meanwhile, the new space will offer room to allow all of our quests to enjoy a daytime or evening meal at a comfortable table. The mood of this nostalgic dining area will be upbeat, high-energy and casual sophistication. This will be a friendly and relaxed place, not fancy or stuffy. The staff will work hard to make you feel at home. The action of the butchers, chefs, and the local crowd and the hustle and bustle of the service staff, will allow you to participate in the energy.

Restaurants.name: Cosmos Ristorante & Pizzeria
Restaurants.description: Cosmos Cafe & Pizzeria offers the finest in authentic and inspired Italian cuisine. Using only the freshest ingredients, our menu features fresh homemade pastas, specialty pizzas, seafood, sandwiches and more! Introducing his family’s generations-old recipes and the experience of his career, owner Gianluca Corso has given Cosmos Italian Cafe and Pizzeria that unique, intimate and irresistible Italian flare that you’ll find nowhere else.

Restaurants.name: Shula's Steak House
Restaurants.description:
Coach Don Shula's ability to dig into the details translated to a record-setting number of wins on the field. His consistent excellence entertained; his pursuit of perfection inspired; and his winning ways created lasting memories. We want every experience at Shula's Steak House to do the same for you.

 

From the moment you enter, Coach's storied career sets the tone for an elevated take on the traditional steakhouse experience. Perfectly prepared steaks, and bold, craveable interpretations of classic steakhouse dishes are paired with attentive service that puts you front and center. We go above and beyond to make sure that each and every carefully considered detail comes together in a way that entertains, not overwhelms, so that you can focus on enjoying the moment and making memories with your guests.  

 

Whether you're celebrating an anniversary or just the end of the work week, your experience at Shula's Steak House will stick with you long after you've left the table.
Restaurants.address: 5111 Tamiami Trl N, North Naples, FL 34103

Restaurants.name: The French
Restaurants.description: Award-winning Chef Vincenzo Betulia offers casual French classics, lighter fare and coastal dishes in an informal, convivial and bustling neighborhood brasserie. The French is a slice of the Belle Epoque in the heart of Naples.

Restaurants.name: BiCE
Restaurants.description: Experience the exquisite decor, tantalizing Italian cuisine and service paralleled to none. An exquisite culinary voyage right to the heart of Italy awaits you amid a decor which combines Old World elegance and modern chic. BiCE Ristorante offers exquisite Northern Italian cuisine, and superb service in an elegant atmosphere. Featuring homemade Pasta, Veal Ossobuco, Veal Chop Milanese and Tiramisu.

Restaurants.name: Caffe Milano
Restaurants.description: Caffé Milano opened its doors in 2015 from a concept inspired by Luca Di Falco, a veteran Managing Partner of BiCE Restaurant, offering a modern take on the classic Naples, presenting italian gourmet in a casual setting. His vision was to delivery the modern but rustic italian cuisine, from the south to the north of Italy. We can delight you with our homemade bread and pastas, our signature skizza (our innovated skinny and light pizza), a wide variety of sandwiches for lunch and authentic italian fresh dishes to satisfy our worldwide clientele all day long. We offer delicious handcrafted drinks and signature desserts such as our giant Tiramisu` or our Homemade Gelato prepared a' la minute. If you are looking for an ideal spot, Caffé Milano should be your first stop of the day and your last stop at night!!!

Restaurants.name: Jane's Cafe
Restaurants.description: A fantastic Downtown Naples Garden location with bubbling Koi Pond on the front Courtyard and cosy garden patio at the back, yet a cool interior to relax in during these hot summer days. Offering Breakfast & Lunch with yummy desserts too. All of our dishes are prepared with totally fresh produce delivered daily, our chefs work with passion to cook made to order plates including vegetarian & vegan meals. Lots of healthy Fruits, homemade Soups, daily Quiche, variety of Eggs Benedicts, Omlettes, delicious Sandwiches & Panini, Seafood Crepes, along with totally comforting French Toast, Crepes, Belgian Waffles, Yogurt Parfaits. All day Brunch is served, sample delightful dishes with a glass of Champagne Cocktail,such as Mimosa, Strawberry Orange Mimosa, our favorite Fruit Lemonade Mocktails, gourmet Espresso drinks or a variety of Teas. Relax with family & friends or simply bring the paper or a good book & enjoy watching the world go by.

Restaurants.name: Alberto's on Fifth Fine Italian Restaurant

photo.caption: The Heart of Downtown Naples, Fifth Avenue

Restaurants.description: WELCOME TO ALBERTOS RESTAURANT Chef Alberto Varetto creates the finest in contemporary Northern Italian cuisine.His culinary interpretations emphasize seasonal ingredients, while creatively respecting the great traditions of Italian gastronomy, The glory of Italian cooking is fresh ingredients, served at their peak and handled in a way that flatters, rather than masks, their personalities.

Restaurants.name: Bleu Provence

photo.caption: Bleu Provence, Award Winning French Restaurant

Restaurants.description: Bleu Provence, Award Winning French Restaurant in Naples, FL. Zagat-Rated and Wine Spectator Grand Award Recipient.

Restaurants.name: Tommy Bahama Restaurant & Bar

photo.caption: As evening falls, this place gets lively

Restaurants.description: Located on charming, historic Third Street South, a short walk from the Naples pier, the original Tommy Bahama Restaurant & Bar is the ideal spot for lunch, dinner, or happy hour. You will instantly feel like a Florida local when treated to unparalleled hospitality on the festive, spacious patio or watch the culinary team in action from a table near the open kitchen.

Restaurants.name: M Waterfront Grille
Restaurants.description: Designed as a contemporary Naples waterfront restaurant, M Waterfront Grille is refined and engaging, featuring Cutting Edge Continental Cuisine with an emphasis on Fresh Seafood, Steaks, Handmade Pasta, Organics and Tapas plates. M Waterfront Grille is both a local favorite as well as a destination restaurant offering dynamic flavor profiles and polished attentive service. The award winning comprehensive Wine List showcases highly allocated vintages and large format selections. Enjoy spectacular Venetian Bay views with Five Unique Venues at the Best Waterfront Restaurant in Naples, FL. View our updated menus on our web site.

Restaurants.name: Molto Trattoria

Restaurants.description: "simply my mom in the kitchen" is our motto and she shares traditional family recipes! All our pastas and sauces are homemade and we pride ourselves on using only the very best quality ingredients. Our pizza chef came all the way from Napoli to create the finest neapolitan pizza for you to enjoy. We invite you to come and dine with us! Serving lunch and dinner. We also offer delivery so you may dine poolside or on the beach.

Restaurants.name: Pazzo! Cucina Italiana
Restaurants.description: Nationally Known ... Locally Loved! Pazzo! is celebrating its 25th year as Naples best, most fun and creative Italian restaurant! With original handcrafted recipes that have stood the test of time along with the sincere friendly service Pazzo! is known for, Pazzo! (which means crazy in Italian) offers a 150 bottle wine list, over 50 unique craft cocktails and spirits along with farm fresh quality ingredients, artisan cheeses, unique small batch olive oils, homemade pasta and the finest quality meats and seafood.

Restaurants.name: Swan River Seafood Restaurant

photo.caption: Lobster Boat Raw Bar. A Naples Icon!!

Restaurants.description: A cozy New England restaurant & raw bar, Swan River Seafood consistently brings the freshest varieties of the sea in delicious ways to happy Naples' locals and visitors. Enjoy wine and oysters at The Lobster Boat Raw Bar and dine on the largest selection of fresh market fish in Naples. The New England vibe continues out to our newly renovated patio booths. Enjoy Florida breezes as you savor the freshest fish with the friendliest service. The seafood market is open daily providing the home cook with pristine fresh fish and delicious prepared delicacies. Visit Swan RIver Seafood for local Stone Crabs October to May.

Restaurants.name: Chops City Grill
Restaurants.description: Our menu features the lowest prices on American, certified Japanese and Australian wagyu steaks, in the country and dry aged Prime beef. The menu is rounded out by affordable “butcher shop” cuts, an array of fresh vegetables, creative entrees, loads of seafood and sushi that can only be complemented by our ‘affordable to extravagant’ wine list, whiskey bar featuring over 100 whiskeys and innovative craft cocktails. Chops City Grill has an elegant dining room that presents our guests with an intimate setting paired with gracious service. With wood paneling, luxurious drapes, relaxed seating and modern lighting this dining room tips its hat to the traditional steak houses of the past.

Restaurants.name: Campiello
Restaurants.description: Housed in Historic Naples Mercantile Building, Campiello offers inventive Italian cuisine inspired by a traditional Tuscan country cooking, with an open kitchen and many wood-roasted and rotisserie-grilled specialties. Join us for the "Italian Taste Tour" - a series of month long culinary salutes to Italy's greatest regions. The restaurant features a lavish interior inspired by Michelangelo-designed Villa San Michele in Friesole, Italy-replete with Murano light fixtures, fine leather chairs and banquettes, polished Venetian plaster, and hand painted Florentine murals

Restaurants.name: Three60 Market
Restaurants.description: Stop by for the best wine prices in Naples! Outside open air seating for breakfast, brunch and lunch on our waterside decks. All staff wear masks. We feature a great wine selection and unique delicacies including artisan cheeses, breads, baked goods, and pastas from Naples Pasta. Breakfast is served 8 till 4, lunch from 11 till 4. Three60 Market has that Southern Florida feeling with a taste of Soho Chic right here on Bayshore Drive in Naples. Everything on our menu is a "creation" - made fresh, from scratch, every day. We promise you an upbeat experience that you won't soon forget whether you come for breakfast or lunch.

Restaurants.name: Brambles English Tea Room
Restaurants.description: English Tea Room serving traditional afternoon teas and a full lunch menus. Over 40 different teas, coffee, soft drinks, wine, champagne and beer

Restaurants.name: Sails Restaurant
Restaurants.description: Opened in February 2018, Sails quickly became the talk of the town, earning the highest accolades possible both from the region’s restaurant reviewers and its discerning patrons. Much of the media's focus is what sets Sails apart: attention to detail at every level throughout the experience. From its exclusively-sourced pristine ingredients to friendly five-star service, co-founding partners Veljko Pavicevic and Corinne Ryan created a dining haute spot where the finest flavors of France, Italy and Greece evoke fond memories of a coastal European getaway with each delicious bite.

Restaurants.name: The Claw Bar
Restaurants.description: The Claw Bar brings chic hotel dining to the Bellasera Resort in downtown Naples. Featuring gracious hospitality and spectacular cuisine, The Claw Bar specializes in seafood towers assembled right before your eyes in our open kitchen, as well as a full array of seafood entrees, southern-influenced dishes, and regionally-inspired cuisine. The Claw Bar prides itself on using locally-grown and locally-sourced ingredients whenever possible. Indoor and outdoor dining options available.
Restaurants.address: 221 9th St S Fl 34102 Located inside the Bellasera Resort, Naples, FL 34102-6258

Restaurants.name: Michelbob's Championship Ribs & Steaks
Restaurants.description: Michelbob's has been family-owned and operated since 1979. Features imported baby back ribs, pulled pork, sliced pork, sliced beef, steaks and homemade onion rings, cole slaw and baked bbq beans. Winner of over 100 awards for great food and voted "Best Restaurant" in S.W. Florida. Casual family dining with a full bar. The decor is worth the trip by itself.

Restaurants.name: Alice Sweetwaters Bar & Grille

photo.caption: Children's chicken strips with fries.... beware, the sauce that comes with it is not ketchup

Restaurants.description: Alice Sweetwater's has been serving locals and tourists in Naples for 31 years. Opening in December 1988 serving our famous lightly battered deep fried shrimp, fresh grouper and oysters along with a fabulous pork tenderloin, fresh salads, great burgers and many other homemade items.
